<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Source Data Structure</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: #fff;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body {
                color: #e0e0e0;
                background: #1a1a1a;
            }
        }

        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .header {
                border-bottom-color: #404040;
            }
        }

        .tree {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            white-space: pre;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .tree {
                background: #2d2d2d;
            }
        }

        .dir {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .dir {
                color: #4a90e2;
            }
        }

        .file {
            color: #333;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .file {
                color: #e0e0e0;
            }
        }

        .special {
            color: #cc6600;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .special {
                color: #ffa726;
            }
        }

        .legend {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            border: 1px solid #b3d9ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .legend {
                background: #1e3a5f;
                border-color: #4a90e2;
            }
        }

        .legend h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0066cc;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .legend h3 {
                color: #4a90e2;
            }
        }

        .legend ul {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        code {
            background: #f1f3f4;
            padding: 0.125rem 0.25rem;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            code {
                background: #404040;
            }
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #333;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            h1, h2, h3 {
                color: #e0e0e0;
            }
        }

        a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #004499;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        a:focus {
            outline: 2px solid #0066cc;
            outline-offset: 2px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            a {
                color: #66b3ff;
            }

            a:hover {
                color: #99ccff;
            }

            a:focus {
                outline-color: #66b3ff;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üìÅ Source Data Structure</h1>
        <p>This tree shows the source data being indexed by web-indexer.<br>
        Special files like <code>.noindex</code> and <code>.skipindex</code> affect indexing behavior.</p>
    </div>

    <p><a href="../">Back to demo list</a></p>

    <div class="tree">{{range .Items}}{{.Indent}}{{.Prefix}}<span class="{{.Class}}">{{.Name}}{{.Suffix}}</span>
{{end}}</div>

    <div class="legend">
        <h3>Control File Legend</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><code>.noindex</code> - Directory is completely excluded from listings and indexing</li>
            <li><code>.skipindex</code> - Directory appears in parent listing but no index page is generated</li>
            <li>No control file - Directory is fully indexed with generated listings</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>